title: Congo presidential election on course for December, says prime minister
text:
Congo presidential election on course for December, says prime minister 1:33pm GMT - 00:48 
The prime minister of the Democratic Republic of Congo confirms the country's election is on course for late December. Rough cut (no reporter narration). ▲ Hide Transcript ▶ View Transcript
